    "description": "Fresh, fiery and fun, you'll love every bite of this 20-minute wonder. You'll stir-fry chicken mince with honey, chilli, lemongrass and lime leaf then serve with sambal veggie rice for a quick win that's packed with nutrients. Under 600 calories.",
