    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with 225ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-and-lemongrass-chicken-mince-stir-fry-and-veggie-rice/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>chicken mince </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-and-lemongrass-chicken-mince-stir-fry-and-veggie-rice/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-and-lemongrass-chicken-mince-stir-fry-and-veggie-rice/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken mince is lightly browned, reduce the heat to medium-high and add the <strong>sliced onion</strong></p><p>Cook for 4-5 min or until softening and the chicken mince is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-and-lemongrass-chicken-mince-stir-fry-and-veggie-rice/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Whilst the onion is softening, top, tail, peel and coarsely grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then thinly slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> spinach</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-and-lemongrass-chicken-mince-stir-fry-and-veggie-rice/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the onion is softening, add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>to the pan with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>lemongrass and lime leaf paste</strong>, <strong>gluten free soy sauce</strong>, <strong>honey </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), stir it all together, cook for 30 secs, then add the <strong>spinach</strong> with a generous splash of <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until the spinach has wilted \u2013 this is your <strong>sticky chilli & lemongrass chicken mince stir fry</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-and-lemongrass-chicken-mince-stir-fry-and-veggie-rice/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, add the <strong>grated carrot</strong> to the pot with your <strong>sambal</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>half</strong> the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> (save the rest for later!) and a a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and cook over a low heat for 1-2 min or until fragrant and the carrot is slightly softened \u2013 this is your <strong>veggie rice</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-and-lemongrass-chicken-mince-stir-fry-and-veggie-rice/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sticky chilli & lemongrass chicken mince stir fry</strong> over the <strong>veggie rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
